        <source>qryVoyageRORODeckItems(_filter : CMQF_VoyageRORODeckItemSummary input; _passport : CM_Passport) : Integer updating;
//----------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created by 	cnwsh3 - 18 October 2011
//
// Implemented version: JMT 7.9.2
// Date  		User  		Change
// 18/10/2011	cnwsh3		CCMS MES 1009 PLAN Interface PAR28479
//----------------------------------------------------------------------
